        <mxCell id="beB2" value="POST /v1/chat                 SSE 流式对话&#10;GET  /v1/confirmations/:id    待确认动作&#10;POST /v1/confirmations/:id    提交确认结果&#10;POST /v1/agent/tools/execute  Runtime 回调&#10;GET  /v1/audit/sessions       会话审计列表&#10;GET  /v1/audit/turns/:id      单轮回放&#10;GET  /v1/inspection/runs      巡检任务&#10;GET  /v1/inspection/runs/:id  巡检报告" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFE6CC;strokeColor=#D79B00;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=10;fontFamily=Courier New" vertex="1" parent="1">
